  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/46a51cf0584c83189ac2f83d9ab41bec28dfb410" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -1.005ex; width:12.421ex; height:2.843ex;" alt="\mathbf {F} =-\mathbf {\nabla } E_{\mathrm {p} }\,."/></span><span about="#mwt148">
